$$\frac{(t^4-5t^3-t^3+5t^2+4t^2-20-4t+20)}{t-5}\leq 0\\ \frac{t^4-6t^3+9t^2-4t}{t-5}\leq 0\\ \frac{t(t^3-6t^2+9t-4)}{t-5}\leq 0\\ \frac{t(t-1)(t^2-5t+4)}{t-5}\leq 0\\ \frac{t(t-1)(t-1)(t-4)}{t-5}\leq 0$$
